  "text": "The maximum observed speed of miracidia in water was about 0.5 mm/s, as calculated from videos of hatching eggs obtained at two separate occasions from experimentally infected mice. This is not very different from the speed reported previously (2 mm/s) [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Both methodological and biological dissimilarities may account for the observed difference.",
